{"tid":846043,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[下週休刊] ONEPIECE 海賊王 920 中文情報","createTime":"2018-10-03T06:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T01:15:04.000Z","uid":130563,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"812bca8451a96930113c05d25aa39c8171a5533b","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"920標題：喜歡御田/關東煮 （下週休刊）<br />\n從錦衛門處得知御田（城）是別名，原名是九里城<br />\n人們喜歡御田，故將其稱為御田城<br />\n御田是當時破天荒的人物，是當時和之國的將軍光月壽喜燒的兒子<br />\n因為多次發生暴力事件，被逐出花之都 和之國有一個號稱「無法無天」的地帶<br />\n各地被放逐的罪人組成黨派，每天都有流血事件發生<br />\n將軍家也對這塊凶惡之地束手無策，那塊地方便是九里<br />\n年輕御田討伐了當時踏入九里的惡黨中最危險的男人『阿修羅童子』<br />\n建造了能提供工作的城市，為了大家又弄了「桃源農莊」，建造了一座有生氣的城市<br />\n御田因此被壽喜燒封為九里大名。此便是御田20歲時的偉業。<br />\n<br />\n此時，索隆路痴犯了<br />\n<br />\n九里的江邊，犬嵐一個人立在那裡，回想與御田的相遇<br />\n當時還是流亡者的犬嵐，因為是頭會說話的狗而遭到旁人的厭惡，只有御田一人例外<br />\n御田責罵了那些閒言碎語的人，對犬嵐非常友善<br />\n<br />\n錦衛門繼續說<br />\n他提到了「受到白鬍子青睞，也讓羅傑喜愛」的武士，談到了事件的核心<br />\n但尾田沒有把核心部分畫出來。總之，御田被定為罪人，被殺了。<br />\n錦衛門流著淚說他死得很壯烈。<br />\n錦衛門等人向御田城趕去，但城池已經被凱多燃起熊熊大火<br />\n當時城裡還有桃之助和他的妹妹日和，和母親光月朱鹮。<br />\n【註：桃之助的媽媽，御田大人的夫人原名光月トキ，トキ的意思是朱鹮，同時和時（toki）的讀音一樣，這應該是尾田玩的諧音梗，和她的能力時時果實（トキトキ能力）相對應】<br />\n有傳言說，朱鹮出生在遙遠的過去，而她自己也可以用時時果實的能力穿越到未來。<br />\n朱鹮在燃燒著熊熊大火的城內，將錦衛門等人送到了未來<br />\n在未來看到荒涼的和之國後，錦衛門以打倒大蛇為目標開始尋找夥伴<br />\n其中有個名為地武衛門的男子來迎接錦衛門，說自己已經等了20年<br />\n決心共同戰鬥的武士們在腳踝上紋上了月亮的印記<br />\n出海的錦衛門在旅行中遇到了路飛<br />\n錦衛門的戰力有草帽一夥，紅心海賊團，毛皮族火槍隊，俠客團，以及有反叛意志的武士們<br />\n他們計畫秘密收集情報，然後取下敵方大將的首級。<br />\n「時間為兩週後，火節的晚上」<br />\n我們要殺入凱多所在的鬼島，取下他的項上人頭！」<br />\n<br />\n下週休刊"},{"pid":"bc407556c59f501a64211710839fcdec0a50b953","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:38:20.000Z","msg":"雖然都預咗下星期休刊架啦...."},{"pid":"61ce4174015245271bdb203c1e2a40c0a29ae647","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"桃之助個老母可能係空白100年嘅人"},{"pid":"02a4411a1ed773d7e9b43beda4308d067c4d6636","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/144831_99d546868cfb5d57c78bb52f2d27d6bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F144831_99d546868cfb5d57c78bb52f2d27d6bf.jpg&h=a797ef81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cf48beec4d92e6927b69a873e3e7ea8a288645d","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"補充今集情報：<br />\n有「在彼此的夢中也在吵架的索隆和山治」嘅劇情...<br />\n<br />\n一睇都覺我on9同gay"},{"pid":"87262ecf78268d1f2b1d7357136fff4aa91767e3","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補充今集情報：<br />\n有「在彼此的夢中也在吵架的索隆和山治」嘅劇情...<br />\n<br />\n一睇都覺<span style=\"color: red;\">得</span>on9同gay</blockquote><br />\n屌"},{"pid":"cf52c45f2fd36e9990b450c23b090a4b3f858913","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee1956a8648709b60e3433c7ab061805bffa14e","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f683e7f9d6960689b29e441d1a41c8b68b2657ac","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:24:10.000Z","msg":"穿越時空果然係果實能力"},{"pid":"cc94a067e6172a5672eedc0629589c617bb345c4","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"02a4411a1ed773d7e9b43beda4308d067c4d6636","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/144831_99d546868cfb5d57c78bb52f2d27d6bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F144831_99d546868cfb5d57c78bb52f2d27d6bf.jpg&h=a797ef81&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:12:29.000Z","msg":"【凱多所在的鬼島現行，桃太郎的故事直接擺上檯面啦&hellip;&hellip;】"},{"pid":"4fe6db9fb6f9b04beb8142c4c2fcd45ce90a698f","tid":846043,"uid":94819,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47a9e90c264fe2c08c3319756e55535ffcf5ea51","tid":846043,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4fe6db9fb6f9b04beb8142c4c2fcd45ce90a698f","tid":846043,"uid":94819,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"咁渣ga"},{"pid":"637ca9f45741efbe2806f04532eb160d65379675","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"應讀者要求畫的扉頁：<br />\n在彼此的夢中也在吵架的索隆和山治，山治和索隆在睡覺並做夢。<br />\n山治夢到自己打敗了索隆，娜美滿是愛意的抱住他。<br />\n索隆夢到自己打敗了山治，喬巴在高興的為他慶祝<br />\n<br />\n<strong>情報圖：</strong><br />\n錦衛門：雖然難以想像&hellip;&hellip;不過有傳聞說，朱鹮殿下是在很久很久以前誕生的人。<br />\n朱鹮：人是絕對無法回到過去的&hellip;但是卻可以去到未來哦&hellip;&hellip;！！我可以憑藉這個不可思議的「時時果實」的能力，到未來的未來旅行<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/204606_0a6d168673042b8eacbf6ed079e0c884.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F204606_0a6d168673042b8eacbf6ed079e0c884.jpg&h=f94dca5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錦衛門：我的主君御田，實在是個史無前例的人物&hellip;他是當時和之國的將軍「光月壽喜燒」大人的兒子，生性無拘無束，一再引發暴力事件，最後終於被逐出了「花之都」&mdash;&mdash;另一方面，當時和之國裡有個號稱「無法無天」的地方&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/204648_49570025870a2a7f0dc2560dc46d90a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F204648_49570025870a2a7f0dc2560dc46d90a4.jpg&h=b60b2791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錦衛門：年輕時的御田大人偏偏要到這「九里」來，和惡黨中最危險的「阿修羅童子」大戰一場&hellip;&hellip;最終將他打敗，並讓所有的流氓都歸順於他 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/204752_6ebafcd2ad71bf7959fc00177b3ac17e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F204752_6ebafcd2ad71bf7959fc00177b3ac17e.jpg&h=d4b6f3d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n &mdash;&mdash;但是凱多的魔爪已經伸到了這裡，城中燃起了大火<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/205019_7aa1790bb44a96576782bd4f27ccc51e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F205019_7aa1790bb44a96576782bd4f27ccc51e.jpg&h=6056c339&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90b80cf2bdb3fda26efa42dcb865e87b2cbf1658","tid":846043,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/205531_38f2f99460378b11adad5e64e6c85328.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F205531_38f2f99460378b11adad5e64e6c85328.jpg&h=b65b19b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三災另外果兩個！？"},{"pid":"e8d2427f38f68f123681a42e331fe4462fe39162","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:09:29.000Z","msg":"講到明唔可以返去過去"},{"pid":"d815806381b66f0b41d03d8b763da3d148bab91e","tid":846043,"uid":738,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37084d8290dc482cea27341f600dd9d07b362fe","tid":846043,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"救艾斯?"},{"pid":"ca0e1dfd5cc2cb8acf55bef6738bd422456b5140","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f37084d8290dc482cea27341f600dd9d07b362fe","tid":846043,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"救艾斯?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"咪講到明唔可以返去過去，上面情報圖有寫"},{"pid":"b26999ef083554a437a147d5007d2df36ad5d1d5","tid":846043,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ca0e1dfd5cc2cb8acf55bef6738bd422456b5140","tid":846043,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f37084d8290dc482cea27341f600dd9d07b362fe","tid":846043,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"救艾斯?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"咪講到明唔可以返去過去，上面情報圖有寫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"明白"},{"pid":"de34b342a19ef2325b9d0b47feb883e63960ea86","tid":846043,"uid":155374,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"最後凱多俾人送咗去未來，唔洗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a437a48026507e6a3cf8021fe68a66a9c4d5ded","tid":846043,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"de34b342a19ef2325b9d0b47feb883e63960ea86","tid":846043,"uid":155374,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"最後凱多俾人送咗去未來，唔洗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"個老母應該係死咗呀嘛"},{"pid":"0a96a9294bc21ac7749aa4385ed66036fab23474","tid":846043,"uid":155374,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2a437a48026507e6a3cf8021fe68a66a9c4d5ded","tid":846043,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"de34b342a19ef2325b9d0b47feb883e63960ea86","tid":846043,"uid":155374,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"最後凱多俾人送咗去未來，唔洗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"個老母應該係死咗呀嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"負皮做咩，惡魔果實會重生㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd585ba79393175aef88ef813b0df680a30de04","tid":846043,"uid":128089,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a96a9294bc21ac7749aa4385ed66036fab23474","tid":846043,"uid":155374,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2a437a48026507e6a3cf8021fe68a66a9c4d5ded","tid":846043,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"de34b342a19ef2325b9d0b47feb883e63960ea86","tid":846043,"uid":155374,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"最後凱多俾人送咗去未來，唔洗打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"個老母應該係死咗呀嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"負皮做咩，惡魔果實會重生㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:22:30.000Z","msg":"唔關我事，我先冇某人咁得閒負皮成個帖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f329ea50f65678797a5407bd120882adce4ff33a","tid":846043,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"我開始懷疑和之國之所以鎖國，好可能係因為空白100年，<br />\n既然和之國又整咗描寫空白100年嘅歷史正文，<br />\n即係話和之國明顯係唔妥空白100年之後成立的世界政府<br />\n拒絕同流合污，而選擇鎖國與世隔絕。"},{"pid":"a0f7cb1c752857e9ab81aecb7e42e40befe03c3f","tid":846043,"uid":150425,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"係咁負皮條撚樣又出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}